:"Lady Mary Isabella Seddinghouse, Baroness Palmer родилась в 1317 г. в местности эаст престон, суссекс, Англия. Её отца звали Sir John Seddinghouse Knight. Она вышла замуж за человека по имени Adam Palmer в 1333 г. в местности ангмиринг, суссекс, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Она умерла в 1380 г. в местности суссекс, Англия в возрасте 63 лет и была похоронена в местности суссекс, Англия."},"sm":{"1317–1380":"1317–1380","1318–1371":"1318–1371","1339–1380":"1339–1380","1300–Male":"1300–Ua Maliu","1337":"1337","1333":"1333","about 1339":"1339","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1371":"1371","1380":"1380","1318":"1318","1317":"1317","1328":"1328","1339":"1339","Angmering, Sussex, England":"Angmering, Sussex, Egelani","Angmering Manor, Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Angmering, Sussex, Egelani, United Kingdom","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Egelani","Steyning, Sussex, England":"Steyning, Sussex, Egelani","East Preston, Sussex, England":"East Preston, Sussex, Egelani"},"sk":{"1317–1380":"1317–1380","1318–1371":"1318–1371","1339–1380":"1339–1380","1300–Male":"1300–Zosnulý","1337":"1337","1333":"1333","about 1339":"1339","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1371":"1371","1380":"1380","1318":"1318","1317":"1317","1328":"1328","1339":"1339","Angmering, Sussex, England":"Angmering, Sussex, England","Angmering Manor, Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Angmering, Sussex, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Sussex, England":"Sussex, England","Steyning, Sussex, England":"Steyning, Sussex, England","East Preston, Sussex, England":"East Preston, Sussex, England"},"es":{"1317–1380":"1317–1380","1318–1371":"1318–1371","1339–1380":"1339–1380","1300–Male":"1300–Fallecido","1337":"1337","1333":"1333","about 1339":"1339","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1371":"1371","1380":"1380","1318":"1318","1317":"1317","1328":"1328","1339":"1339","Angmering, Sussex, England":"Angmering, Sussex, Inglaterra","Angmering Manor, Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Angmering, Sussex, Inglaterra, Reino Unido","Sussex, Engl